h4. Description:

As a Jira administrator, I would like to be able to be able to filter the current set of archived issues by date resolved which is not possible in the _Archived issues_ page. This will support an archival and deletion strategy.
h4. Workaround:
 # Query the issue table:
{code:sql}
select * from jiraissue where archived = 'Y' order by resolutiondate asc;
{code}
 # Export to CSV and analyze externally.
